    "The Chinese Ministry of Education, acknowledging the importance of this educational model, has initiated programs that introduce new opportunities across schools and colleges in the country (Xiaoqing and Rauf, 2023).",
    "These initiatives represent a significant shift from traditional teaching methods, emphasizing integrating science, technology, engineering, and mathematics into a cohesive learning paradigm that prepares students for the demands of the modern workforce.",
    "However, despite these advances, the lack of a cohesive national strategy has resulted in inconsistencies across regions, particularly in aligning teacher development with societal needs.",
    "Publishing a \"white paper\" was a significant step in starting a systematic professional development process in STEM (Zheng et al. 2022).",
    "This has led to specialized training for educators and teachers to adapt to this modern teaching method."
